                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Proton-singles events and",
                "proton-gamma coincidence events were collected using",
                "the Silicon Telescope Array for Reaction Studies,",
                "consisting of telescopes dE-E1-E2 with thickness of",
                "500 mu-m, 1000 mu-m and 1000 mu-m. The dE detector",
                "was segmented into 48 rings (0.5 mm wide) and 16",
                "sectors (each spanning 22.5 deg). The E1 and E2",
                "detectors were operated with a 2x coarser segmentation."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma rays were detected using five clover",
                "high-purity germanium detectors with bismuth-",
                "germanate-oxide (BGO) Compton-suppression shields of",
                "the Livermore-Berkeley Array for Collaborative",
                "Experiments (LiBerACE)"
              ]
            }
